# AWS Auto Scaling Group Project

## Overview
Demonstrated the self-healing and dynamic scaling capabilities of AWS 
EC2 Auto Scaling Groups by manually terminating instances and adjusting 
desired capacity — proving ASG automatically maintains availability 
without human intervention.

